    "description_long": "This is a compact, two-door sports car with a striking blue exterior and a sleek, aerodynamic profile. The car features a prominent rear spoiler, gold multi-spoke alloy wheels, and black accents along the lower body and hood. Its windows are tinted black, and the front end is equipped with aggressive headlights and a vented hood, suggesting high performance. The rear showcases dual exhausts and detailed taillights, emphasizing its sporty character. The bodywork is smooth and glossy, with sharp lines and a low stance typical of modern urban sports cars. The overall design suggests a focus on speed, agility, and visual impact.",
